nodes.text: Greth Lan-Dwu Corp. electrical power-generating plant

The Greth Lan-Dwu Corp. electrical power-generating plant was a Greth Lan-Dwu Corp. facility in Coruscant which generated electricity for Coruscant. Bounty hunter Zam Wesell fired upon the power couplings in an attempt to electrocute Jedi Obi-Wan Kenobi and Anakin Skywalker during their pursuit.
